      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "If your dream is to own the world's nicest Toyota Tercel or Ford Aspire, go for it. We'll always encourage you to chase your dreams. And when you finally track down that dream machine, make sure you savor every bite of ice cream.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
